title: Nikon AF-S Nikkor 70-200mm f/2.8E
description: This new Nikon 70-200mm lens was called 'outstanding in its class' by our reviewer and has super smooth focus and zoom rings. It features super effective vibration reduction, a high-quality construction and superb optical qualities. There are 22 elements in 18 groups, including 6 Extra Low Dispersion,1 Flourite and one High Refractive Index element.

title: Nikor  19mm
description: As the first PC-NIKKOR to employ two PC rotation mechanisms, this lens takes flexibility to a new level. Ideal for architectural, fine art, and landscape photography, it’s made for photographers who have a keen sense of space.
